  "task": "Parse and balance-validate an X12 EDI 835 ERA (Electronic Remittance Advice). Emit normalized JSON: { format, payer, payee, payment, claims, provider_adjustments, balance_check }. Balance-check the sum of CLP payments + PLB adjustments against the BPR declared total.",
